name: CubicTez #34
description:
"CubicTez" is a collection of unique 3D characters, each one with a unique look and different patterns. 
Each character has its own story behind it. I have tried to make the CubicTez collection as an album and souvenir of NFT artists and people whose art I like 

In fact ,CubicTez is a collection of memories from the NFT world on the blockchain which I think will last forever.

resolution : 4000x4000
